snippet.title: Crystal Caves HD Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: The greatest miner in the galaxy is back! Revisit the 3 original episodes in spectacular HD and guide Mylo through a brand new episode featuring new enemies, break away platforms and new biomes! Ramp up the excitement and compete against your friends on the online leaderboards, and collect all 32 achievements.
